# Auth Rules

## Overview

Authentication for the Server Manager web UI.

## Patterns

- Protect routes requiring authentication
- Handle auth state in client components
- Secure API routes with middleware

## Security

- Never expose credentials in client code
- Use HTTP-only cookies for session tokens
- Validate auth state server-side

## Implementation

```ts
// Auth check pattern
async function requireAuth() {
  const session = await getSession();
  if (!session) {
    redirect('/login');
  }
  return session;
}
```
